                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Saldırı</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1 </span><span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Su Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir.</span></p>",
